# GASLIT LiveKit / voice rules

- **Rooms:** `attacker_room` (MINJA / attacker line), `forensic_room` (operator forensic Q&A).
- **Transcripts** go to FastAPI only: `POST /api/voice-input` and `POST /api/forensic-qa`. Do not send secrets to the browser beyond LiveKit + ElevenLabs **public** agent id.
- **Tokens:** Browser obtains JWT via `POST /api/livekit/token` (server holds `LIVEKIT_API_KEY` / `LIVEKIT_API_SECRET`).
- **ElevenLabs:** Dossier audio = **Flash v2.5** via `POST /api/voice/tts`. Conv AI widget uses `NEXT_PUBLIC_ELEVENLABS_AGENT_ID` only. **No voice cloning** of the attacker — LiveKit audio is for transcription / demo only (PRD Q&A).
- **Fallback:** `public/fixtures/attacker.wav` + hardcoded transcript (PRD §15); key **F** on operator page.

When in doubt, read [docs/contracts.md](docs/contracts.md) and [GASLIT_PRD_v6.md](GASLIT_PRD_v6.md).
